		<body>
			<div type="transcription">
				<div type="original" xml:lang="yi">
					<pb facs="EHRI-ET-YV3540549_01.jpg" n="1"/>
					<p><term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-687" type="subject">גבית עדות</term> אויפגענומען דורך <persName ref="#ehri_et_mamet_efraim_fishl">אפרים פישל מאַמעט</persName></p>
					<p><persName ref="#ehri_et_amarnikh_rokhl">אמארניך רחל</persName> געבוירן דעם 1926 xii/7 אין <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/764862/miedzyrzec-podlaski.html">מעזריטש</placeName> אין <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/798544/republic-of-poland.html">פוילין</placeName>
						דערציילט: דעם 25/1943 זיינען מיר 20 <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1207" type="subject">מענטשן</term> דערונטער <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-826" type="subject">מענער</term>
						<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-825" type="subject">פרויען</term> און 3 <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-824" type="subject">קינדער</term> פון 4-15 יאָר די עלטער, געלעגן <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-262" type="subject">אויסבאהאלטן</term> ביי אונז אין שטוב אין א <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-265" type="subject">בונקער</term>. די <term ref="#ehri_et_nationalities_germans"
							>דייטשן</term> האבן דערווישט אונזער <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-265" type="subject">באעלטעניש</term>, אויפגעריסן די פאדלאגע מיט אייזן שטאבעס און זיך אריינגעקראגן צו אונז: מיר האבן <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1053" type="subject">אונזערע לעבענס געפרובט אויסקויפן</term> פאר געלד. מיר האבן זיי געגעבן גאָלד מיט דאלארן אין ווערט פון 200,000 <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/798544/republic-of-poland.html"
							>פוילישע</placeName> זלאָטעס, <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-660" type="subject">צוגענומען דאס געלד</term>, האבן זיי <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-532" type="subject">דערשאסן</term> אויפן ארט א <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-825" type="subject">פרוי</term> מיט א <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-826" type="subject">מאַן</term>, איך און נאָך 2 <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-824"
							type="subject">מיידלאַך</term> זיינען מיר אנטלאָפן, די איבריקע 15 זיינען מיטגענומען געוואָרן און <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-518" type="subject">אוועקגעפיהרט</term> געוואָרן. מיר האבן אנגעטראפן איין אָפענע <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-265" type="subject">בונקער</term> דאָרט זיינען מיר אריין און אבסערווירט די <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-550" type="subject">אקציע</term>. דאס איז שוין געווען די לעצטע <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-550" type="subject">אקציע</term> ביי אונז אין שטאדט. אידן איז דאַן שוין געווען בסך הכל 5.000. מיר האבן געזעהען ווי צום הערשט האבן די <orgName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/authorities/ehri_cb-429">ס"ס</orgName>
						צוגענומען מיט כֹח ביי <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-825" type="subject">פרויען</term> אירע <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-824" type="subject">קינדער</term> אוועקגעפיהרט אויפן <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-747" type="subject">בית עולם</term> און זיי דאָרט <term ref="#EHRI-ET-YV3540549_2" rend="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-532" type="subject">געשאָסן</term>. די איבריגע <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1207" type="subject">מענטשן</term>
						<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-825" type="subject">פרויען</term> און <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-826" type="subject">מענער</term> זיינען געבליבן אויפן פאליציי-פלאץ אויף <placeName
							ref="http://www.geonames.org/756135/warsaw.html">פיעקאַרסגא-גאס</placeName>. דאס איז געווען א גרויסע פלאַץ אין מיטן שטאט ארומגערינגעלט מיט מויערן דארט האט זיך געפונען די <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-480" type="subject"
							>יידישע-געטא-מיליץ</term>. אויפן פלאַץ איז פארגעקומען א <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-411" type="subject">סעלעקציע</term>. עטלעכע <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-825" type="subject">פרויען</term> און <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-826" type="subject">מענער</term> אנערך 1.200 <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1207" type="subject">מאַן</term> זיינען זאָפאָרט <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-532" type="subject">דערשאָסן</term> געוואָרן, די איבריקע <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-518" type="subject">אפגעפיהרט</term> געווארן קיין <placeName
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_camps-2032" type="camp">טרעמבלינקי</placeName> און <placeName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_camps-560" type="camp">מאַידאַנעק</placeName>. די <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-550" type="subject">אקציע</term> האט געדויערט אזוי 3 טעג. ווען ס'איז שטיל געוואָרן זיינען די <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-262" type="subject">אויסבאהאַלטענע</term> ארויס פון זייערע
							<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-265" type="subject">באַעלטענישן</term>. צווישן זיי אויך איך און מיין <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-822" type="subject">מוטער</term> וועלכע האט איז <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-262" type="subject">אויסבאהאַלטן</term> אין אן אנדער <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-265" type="subject">בונקער</term>, דאַן זיינען מיר דעם 28טן מאַי געכאַפט געוואָרן דוכט <term
							ref="#ehri_et_nationalities_germans">דייטשן</term> און <term ref="#ehri_et_nationalities_ukrainians" type="subject">אוקראַאינער</term> און <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-518" type="subject">אפגעפיהרט</term> געוואָרן קיין <placeName
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_camps-560" type="camp">מאַידאַניק</placeName>. געפיהרט זיינען מיר געווארן אין <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-522" type="subject">פערמאכטע וואַגאָנס</term> צו 150 <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1207" type="subject">מענטשן</term> אין א <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-522" type="subject">וואַגאָן</term>. דער גאַנצער טראַנספאָרט אונזערער האט געציילט אנערך 1000 מאן. אנקומענדיק קיין
							<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_camps-560" type="subject">מאַידַנעק</term> איז פארגעקומען א <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-411" type="subject">סעלעקציע</term>. עלטערע <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-826" type="subject">מענער</term> און <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-825" type="subject">פרויען</term> גלייך אין <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-501"
							type="subject">אויווען</term> אריין צווישן וועלכע ס'איז געווען אויך מיין <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-822" type="subject">מוטער</term>. <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-824" type="subject">קינדער</term> זיינען
						אויך גלייך געגאנגען מיט די עלטערע אין <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-501" type="subject">קרעמאַטוריום</term>. איך בין פארעכענט געוואָרן צווישן די געזונטע וועלכע זיינען גענומען געוואָרן אויף <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-943" type="subject">ארבעט</term> אין <placeName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_camps-560" type="camp">מאַידאַנעק</placeName>. דער <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-508"
							type="subject">ארבייטס-לאַגער</term> איז געווען אנערך 250 מ"ר פון פלאץ פון די <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-501" type="subject">קרעמיטאריומ'ס</term> און <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-499" type="subject">גאז
							אויווענס</term>. דער סדר היום אין <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-508" type="subject">לאַגער</term> איז געווען אזעלכער: 31/2 דעם זייגער פריה איז געווען דער <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-487" type="subject"
							>אפעל</term>. נישט <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1207" type="subject">איינער</term> איז ארויס פון <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-837" type="subject">באַראַק</term>
						<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-836" type="subject">באָרוועס</term> און געשטאַנען אזוי אויפ'ן <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-831" type="subject">פראסט און שניי</term> ביז זייגער 6. די <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-292" type="subject">קראַנקע</term> פלעגט מען צום <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-487" type="subject">אפעל</term> ארויסטראָגן און לייגן אויף אויסגעשפרייטע קאָצן. נישט איינער פון די <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-292" type="subject">קראַנקע</term> פלעגט זיך בעטן ס'זאָל פארקומען א <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-411" type="subject">סעלעקציע</term> און ער זאָל שוין קענען גייען אין <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-501" type="subject">קראמאַטאָריום</term>, וואס וועט מאכן אנ'ענדע צו זיינע יסורים. דאַן פלעגט</p>
					<p><pb facs="EHRI-ET-YV3540549_02.jpg" n="2"/></p>
					<p>אונז אויף <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-832" type="subject">פרישטיק</term> געבן צו טרינקען אביסל <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-832" type="subject">רומיאַניק</term> און דאָס איז געווען אונזער <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-832" type="subject">ערנעהרונג</term> ביז מיטאָג. 12 א זייגער איז געקומען א <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-832" type="subject">זופע פון וואַסער</term>. 6 איז פארגעקומען דער נאַכט-<term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-487" type="subject">אַפעל</term> ביי וועלכען מיר פלעגן אפשטיין אויף די פיס נאָך א גאנצן טאָג <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-943" type="subject">ארבעט</term> 2 טיילמאָהל 3 שעה, ווייל
						אָפט פלעגן פאָרקומען קאַרנע-<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-487" type="subject">אפעלען</term> וואס דויערט פיל לענגער צוליבן <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-562" type="subject">שלאָגן</term> און <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-532" type="subject">הרג'נן</term> די <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-650" type="subject">העפטלינגע</term> ערשט דאַן האבן מיר געקראגן 80 גר' <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-832" type="subject">ברויט</term>, 10 גר' <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-832" type="subject">מארגערין</term> און <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-832"
							type="subject">שוואַרצע קאַפע</term>. אונזער <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-943" type="subject">ארבייט</term> איז געווען א שווער פיזישע ביי שטיין-האַקעריי טראָגן ציגל ברעטער און אנדערע פיזישע <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-943" type="subject">מלאכות</term>. אין <placeName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_camps-560" type="camp">מאַידאַנעק</placeName> בין איך אפגעווען 6 וואכן. דעם 16טן יולי 1943 זיינען מיר געזונטע <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-825" type="subject">פרויען</term> און <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-826" type="subject">מענער</term>
						<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-518" type="subject">איבערגעפיהרט</term> געוואָרן קיין <placeName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_camps-1869" type="camp">סקאַרזשיסקאָ קאַמיעננאַ</placeName> ביי <placeName
							ref="http://www.geonames.org/760778/radom.html">ראַדאָם</placeName>, <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/769250/kielce.html">קעלצער וואיעוואודשאַפט</placeName>. דאָרט האבן מיר <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-943" type="subject"
							>געארבייט</term> אין איין אמוניציע-<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-929" type="subject">פאבריק</term> געהייסן האט די פאבריק שמוצ'ס <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-929" type="subject">פאבריק</term> דער נומר 84 ALE.
							<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-943" type="subject">געארבייט</term> האבן מיר 12 שעה אין טאָג פון 6 ביז 6. פריה זייגער 4 איז פארגעקומען דער <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-487" type="subject">אפעל</term> פאַרנאַכט
						פלעגט ער דויער'ן ביז 8. ביי א קארנע-<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-487" type="subject">אפעל</term> ביז 9 האלב 10 פלעג דויערן אזאַ פארנאכטיקער אפעל. די פארפלעגונג: 80 גר' <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-832"
							type="subject">ברויט</term>. מיטאג: צוויי <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-832" type="subject">זופעס פון וואַסער</term> מיט <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-832" type="subject">פארעפֿולטע בוראַקעס</term>, ווי אויך
						אויף 10 גר' <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-832" type="subject">מאַרמאָלאַד</term>. אויסגעארבייט האבן מיר גראַנאַטן און סיי נאַבאָיעס פון 2 צמ"טר. פון אויפרייס מאטעריאַל פלעגן אפט <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1207" type="subject">מענטשן</term>
						<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-745" type="subject">געהרגט</term> ווערן. פון פיקרינע (אַזאַ מאטעריאַל וואס קומט אריין אין די גראַנאַטן) זיינען מענטשען גענצליך געל געווארן. ס'פלעגן אויך פאָרקומען <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-411" type="subject">סעלעקציעס</term>. די שוואַכסטע פלעגט ניט פיהרן אין <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-501" type="subject">קרעמאַטאָריומס</term>, וואס איז דאַן ניט געווען, נור אויף די
						שטשעלניצעס פלעגט זיי <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-532" type="subject">שיסן</term>. פון 540 <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1207" type="subject">מענטשן</term> צווישן זיי 120 <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-825" type="subject">פרויען</term>, זיינען ביים לעבן געבליבן 40 <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-826" type="subject">מענער</term> און ביי די 60 <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-825" type="subject">פרויען</term>. מיטן דערנהענטער'ן זיך פון <term ref="#ehri_et_nationalities_russians">רוסישן</term>-פראָנט זיינען מיר נאָכן אָפזיין דאָרטן 14 מאָנאט אין סעפטעמבער מאָנאַט 1944 צוזאַמען מיטן גאנצן
							<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-567" type="subject">לאַגער</term>
						<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-623" type="subject">עוואַקואירט</term> געוואָרן קיין <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/2879139/leipzig.html">לייפציק</placeName>. אויך אין א אמוניציע <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-929" type="subject">פאבריק</term> געהייסן האט זי SC ALE 1. דא האבן מיר <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-943" type="subject">געארבעט</term> ביי עטוואָס בעסערע <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-831" type="subject">לעבענ'ס באדינגונגן</term>, <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-411" type="subject">סעלעקציעס</term> פלעגן אבער פארקומען פון צייט צו צייט פלעגט מען די שוואכערע ארויסנעמען
						און <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-518" type="subject">אוועקפיהרן</term>, גענוי וואוּ וויס איך נישט. אזוי זיינען מיר דאָרט אפגעווען גאנצע 9 מאָנאט. אין אפריל מאנאט 1945 ווען די <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1029"
							type="subject">אמעריקאנער ארמיי</term> האט זיך גענומען דערנעהנטער'ן קיין <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/2879139/leipzig.html">לייפציג</placeName> האט מען אונז ביינאכט ארויסגעפיהרט פון די <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-837"
							type="subject">באַראַקען</term> צוזאַמען מיט די <orgName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/authorities/ehri_cb-429">ס"ס</orgName> לייט האבן מיר גענומען <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-517" type="subject">וואַנדערן</term> צופוס איבער די
						פעלדער און וועלדער פון <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/2921044/federal-republic-of-germany.html">דייטשלאַנד</placeName>. ווו צו <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-623" type="subject">עוואקואירן</term> אונז איז שוין ניט געווען ווייל דאס <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1080" type="subject">מלחמה</term>-פייער האט שוין געהאַט ארומגעכאַפט אלע ווינקעלאַך פון <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/2921044/federal-republic-of-germany.html">דייטשלאנד</placeName>, האבן מיר זיך אזוי
						ארומגעשלעפט <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-517" type="subject">3 וואכן</term>. די 250 גר' <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-832" type="subject">ברויט</term> אויפן וועג, וואס מ'האט אונז מיטגעגעבן פארלאזנדיג <placeName
							ref="http://www.geonames.org/2879139/leipzig.html">לייפציג</placeName> האט זיך שוין לאנג געהאַט געענדיגט פלעגן מיר עסען <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-832" type="subject">גראָז</term> און <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-832" type="subject">רויע קאַרטאָפל</term> פון די פעלדער. פלעגן דאס באמערקען די נאַציס האָט אויף אונז <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-532" type="subject">געשאָסן</term> און ניט איינער איז
							<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-532" type="subject">געהרג'ט</term> געוואָרן ביים לויפן כאַפן די <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-832" type="subject">רויע קאַרטאָפל</term> אדער גראָז פון פעלד. די <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-637" type="subject">ארומיקע פויערים</term></p>
					<p><pb facs="EHRI-ET-YV3540549_03.jpg" n="3"/></p>
					<p>פלעגן די <orgName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/authorities/ehri_cb-429">ס"ס</orgName> ווארענען זיי זאלען זיך היטן פאר די <q>שטוילייז</q> ד.ה. די גנבים וואס זיי פיהרען. גענומען האט מען אונז פון <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/2879139/leipzig.html"
							>לייפציג</placeName> 12.000 <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1207" type="subject">מאַן</term>, זעענדיק אז ס'איז שווערליך צו וואַנדערן אזא גרויסע מחנה האָט אונז אוועקגעטיילט אין גרופעס און יעדע גרופע האָט <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-517" type="subject">געוואַנדערט</term> אין איין אנדער ריכטונג. דער <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-477" type="subject">קאמענדאַנט פון לאַגער</term> פלעגט מיט אַ טאַקסע און אין דער האַנד
						אַ מאַפ ארומפאָהרן פון גרופע צו גרופע און ווּ דער <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-477" type="subject">איבערשארשפיהרער</term> פלעגט הייסן דאָרט פלעגט מען אונז פיהרן. געוועהנליך זיינען דאס געווען פלעצער ווו דאס <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1080" type="subject">מלחמה</term>-פייער איז נאָך געווען אביסל ווייטליך. מיין גרופע האט געציילט 4.000 <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-825" type="subject">פרויען</term> געבליבן ביים לעבן
						זיינען 1.200. אונזער גרופע איז געווען מערסטענס פון יידישע <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-825" type="subject">פרויען</term> פון <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/798544/republic-of-poland.html">פוילן</placeName> און <placeName
							ref="http://www.geonames.org/8505031/czechoslovakia.html">טשעכיען</placeName>. אזוי ארום האבן מיר <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-517" type="subject">אדורכגעמאַכט צופוס</term> 600 קל"מ. אדורכגעגאנגען זיינען מיר גאנץ <placeName
							ref="http://www.geonames.org/2842566/saxony.html">זאַקסן</placeName>, און צוזאַמען מיט די <orgName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/authorities/ehri_cb-429">ס"ס לייט</orgName>
						<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-262" type="subject">זיך אויסבאהאלטן</term> פון די <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1078" type="subject">אַלירטע ארמייען</term>. ווען די <orgName
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/authorities/ehri_cb-429">ס"ס לייט</orgName> האבן שוין ניט געהאַט מער ווו אונז צו פיהרן, האבן זיי אונז געלאזן אונטער'ן פרייען הימל און די <term ref="#ehri_et_nationalities_russians">רוסן</term> האבן אונז דעם 7/1945 (מאָנטיק איז עס
						געווען) <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-573" type="subject">באפרייט</term> אין <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/2916851/grossdorf.html">גראָדאָרף</placeName> ביי <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/2955770/apolda.html"
							>אַפאָלדאָ</placeName> אין <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/2842566/saxony.html">זאַקסן</placeName>.</p>
					<p><persName ref="#ehri_et_amarnikh_rokhl">אמארניך רחל</persName></p>
				</div>
				<div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
					<pb facs="EHRI-ET-YV3540549_01.jpg" n="1"/>
					<p><term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-687" type="subject">Testimony</term> taken by <persName ref="#ehri_et_mamet_efraim_fishl">Efraim Fishl Mamet</persName></p>
					<p><persName ref="#ehri_et_amarnikh_rokhl">Amarnikh, Rokhl</persName>, born <date when="1926-12-07">December 7, 1926</date> in <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/764862/miedzyrzec-podlaski.html">Międzyrzec</placeName>, <placeName
							ref="http://www.geonames.org/798544/republic-of-poland.html">Poland</placeName>, relates: On <date when="1943-05-25">May 25, 1943</date>, we were twenty <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1207" type="subject">people</term>, among them <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-826" type="subject">men</term>, <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-825" type="subject">women</term>, and three <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-824"
							type="subject">children</term> aged from four to fifteen years old, lying <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-262" type="subject">hidden</term> in our house in a <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-265" type="subject"
							>bunker</term>. The <term ref="#ehri_et_nationalities_germans">Germans</term> discovered our <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-265" type="subject">hiding place</term>, tore up the floor with iron bars, and managed to reach us: we tried to <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1053" type="subject">buy our lives</term> with money. We gave them gold and dollars to the value of 200,000 <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/798544/republic-of-poland.html">Polish</placeName> zlotys, <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-660" type="subject">they took the money</term> and <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-532" type="subject">shot</term> a <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-825"
							type="subject">woman</term> and a <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-826" type="subject">man</term> on the spot. I fled together with another two <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-824" type="subject">girls</term>. The
						remaining fifteen were taken and <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-518" type="subject">deported</term>. We found an open <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-265" type="subject">bunker</term> and went in. From there
						observed the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-550" type="subject">aktion</term>. This was the last <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-550" type="subject">aktion</term> in our city. There were then in total 5,000 Jews
						therein. We saw how at first the <orgName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/authorities/ehri_cb-429">SS</orgName> [men] took the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-824" type="subject">children</term> from the <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-825" type="subject">women</term> by force and drove them to the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-747" type="subject">cemetery</term>, where they <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-532" type="subject">shot</term> them. The remaining <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1207" type="subject">people</term>, <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-826"
							type="subject">men</term> and <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-825" type="subject">women</term>, remained in the Politzei Sqaure on <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/756135/warsaw.html">Piekarsga Street</placeName>. This was a large
						square in the middle of the city surrounded with walls; the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-480" type="subject">Jewish-ghetto police</term> was located there. In the square a <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-411"
							type="subject">selection</term> took place. Some <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-825" type="subject">women</term> and <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-826" type="subject">men</term>, around 1,200 <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1207" type="subject">persons</term>, were <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-532" type="subject">shot</term> straight away, the rest were <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-518" type="subject">taken away</term> to <placeName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_camps-2032" type="camp">Treblinka</placeName> and <placeName
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_camps-560" type="camp">Majdanek</placeName>. The <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-550" type="subject">aktion</term> continued in this way for three days. When the situation calmed, those in
							<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-262" type="subject">hiding</term> came out of their <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-265" type="subject">hiding places</term>, among them also I and my <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-822" type="subject">mother</term>, who had <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-262" type="subject">hidden</term> in a different <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-265" type="subject">bunker</term>. Then, on <date when="1943-05-28">May 28</date>, we were caught by <term ref="#ehri_et_nationalities_germans">Germans</term> and <term ref="#ehri_et_nationalities_ukrainians"
							>Ukrainians</term> and <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-518" type="subject">deported</term> to <placeName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_camps-560" type="camp">Majdanek</placeName>. We were <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-518" type="subject">transported</term> in <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-522" type="subject">closed wagons</term>, up to 150 <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1207" type="subject">people</term> in a <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-522" type="subject">wagon</term>. Arriving in <placeName
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_camps-560" type="camp">Majdanek</placeName>, a <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-411" type="subject">selection</term> took place. Old <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-826" type="subject">men</term> and <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-825" type="subject">women</term> went straight to the <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-501" type="subject">oven</term>, among them also my <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-822" type="subject">mother</term>. <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-824"
							type="subject">Children</term> also went directly with the elderly to the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-501" type="subject">crematorium</term>. I was deemed to be among the healthy ones, who were taken for <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-943" type="subject">work</term> in <placeName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_camps-560" type="camp">Majdanek</placeName>. The <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-508"
							type="subject">work camp</term> was around 250 meters from the place of the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-501" type="subject">crematoria</term> and <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-499" type="subject">gas
							ovens</term>. The daily schedule in the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-508" type="subject">camp</term> was as follows: the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-487" type="subject">roll call</term> took place at 3.30
						AM. Many <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1207" type="subject">people</term> came out of the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-837" type="subject">barracks</term>
						<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-836" type="subject">barefoot</term> and stood in the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-831" type="subject">frost and snow</term> until 6 Am. We would drag out the <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-292" type="subject">sick</term> to the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-487" type="subject">roll call</term> and lay them on blankets spread out on the floor. More than one of the <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-292" type="subject">sick</term> would beg for <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-411" type="subject">selection</term> so that he could go to the <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-501" type="subject">crematorium</term>, putting an end to his suffering.</p>
					<p><pb facs="EHRI-ET-YV3540549_02.jpg" n="2"/></p>
					<p>For <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-832" type="subject">breakfast</term> they would give us to drink a bit of <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-832" type="subject">chamomile</term> [brew] and this was our <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-832" type="subject">nourishment</term> until midday. Twelve noon there was a <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-832" type="subject">watery soup</term>. At 6 PM was the night time <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-487" type="subject">roll call</term>, at which we would stand on our feet after an entire day at <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-943" type="subject">work</term>, sometimes three hours,
						because punishment <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-487" type="subject">roll calls</term> often took place and these lasted much longer due the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-562" type="subject">beating</term> and
							<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-532" type="subject">killing</term> of the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-650" type="subject">prisoners</term>, only then did we receive 80 grams of <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-832" type="subject">bread</term>, ten grams of <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-832" type="subject">margarine</term> and <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-832"
							type="subject">black coffee</term>. Our <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-943" type="subject">work</term> was hard physical <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-556" type="subject">labor</term>, hacking stones, dragging
						brick boards and other physical <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-943" type="subject">labor</term>. I was in <placeName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_camps-560" type="camp">Majdanek</placeName> for six weeks. On <date
							when="1943-07-16">July 16, 1943</date>, we healthy <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-825" type="subject">women</term> and <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-826" type="subject">men</term> were <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-518" type="subject">transported</term> to <placeName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_camps-1869" type="camp">Skarżysko-Kamienna</placeName> near <placeName
							ref="http://www.geonames.org/760778/radom.html">Radom</placeName> in the <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/769250/kielce.html">Kielce Voivodship</placeName>. There we <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-943" type="subject">worked</term> in
						an ammunition <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-929" type="subject">factory</term> which was called Shmutz’s <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-929" type="subject">factory</term>, number ALE 84. We <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-943" type="subject">worked</term> twelve hours per day from 6 AM to 6 PM. At 4 AM a <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-487" type="subject">roll call</term> took place, at night it would
						last until 8 PM. A punishment <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-487" type="subject">roll call</term> would last until 9 or 9.30 PM. The nourishment: 80 grams of <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-832" type="subject"
							>bread</term>. Midday: two <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-832" type="subject">watery soups</term> with <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-832" type="subject">rotting beats</term>, as well as 10 grams of <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-832" type="subject">marmalade</term>. We made grenades and 2 centimeter bullets. <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1207" type="subject">People</term> were often <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-745" type="subject">killed</term> by exploding material. Some became completely yellow due to the picric acid (such a material which is put into the grenades). <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-411" type="subject">Selections</term> also took place. The weak would not be taken to <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-501" type="subject">crematoria</term>, since there were none, but
						would be <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-532" type="subject">shot</term> at the firing range. Out of 540 <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1207" type="subject">people</term>, among them 120 <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-825" type="subject">women</term>, 40 <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-826" type="subject">men</term> remained alive and among the <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-825" type="subject">women</term> 60. As the <term ref="#ehri_et_nationalities_russians">Russian</term> front neared, after we have been there fourteen months, in <date when="1944-09">September 1944</date>, we were
							<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-623" type="subject">evacuated</term> to <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/2879139/leipzig.html">Leipzig</placeName> together with the entire <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-567" type="subject">camp</term>. Also to an ammunition <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-929" type="subject">factory</term>, which was called SC ALE 1. There we <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-943" type="subject">worked</term> in somewhat better <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-831" type="subject">living conditions</term>, however <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-411" type="subject">selections</term> took place from time to time, the weaker would be taken away and <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-518" type="subject">deported</term>, exactly to
						where I do not know. We were there for nine whole months. In <date when="1945-04">April 1945</date>, when the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1029" type="subject">American army</term> began to near <placeName
							ref="http://www.geonames.org/2879139/leipzig.html">Leipzig</placeName>, they took us out of the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-837" type="subject">barracks</term> at night and, together with the <orgName
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/authorities/ehri_cb-429">SS</orgName> men, we started <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-517" type="subject">wandering</term> on foot over the fields and forests of <placeName
							ref="http://www.geonames.org/2921044/federal-republic-of-germany.html">Germany</placeName>. There was already nowhere to <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-623" type="subject">evacuate</term> us to because the fire of <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1080" type="subject">war</term> had reached all corners of <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/2921044/federal-republic-of-germany.html">Germany</placeName>, they dragged us around like this for <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-517" type="subject">three weeks</term>. The 250 grams of <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-832" type="subject">bread</term> for the journey, which they gave us when we left <placeName
							ref="http://www.geonames.org/2879139/leipzig.html">Leipzig</placeName>, had already run out long ago, we would eat <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-832" type="subject">grass</term> and <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-832" type="subject">raw potatoes</term>. When the Nazis noticed this, they would <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-532" type="subject">shoot</term> at us, and more than one person was
							<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-532" type="subject">killed</term> running to grab <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-832" type="subject">potatoes</term> or grass form a field. The <orgName
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/authorities/ehri_cb-429">SS</orgName> would</p>
					<p><pb facs="EHRI-ET-YV3540549_03.jpg" n="3"/></p>
					<p>warn the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-637" type="subject">surrounding peasants</term> that they should beware of the stoylayz, meaning the thieves that they were driving onwards. They took from <placeName
							ref="http://www.geonames.org/2879139/leipzig.html">Leipzig</placeName> 12,000 <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1207" type="subject">persons</term>. Seeing that it was difficult to wander around with such a large group, they divided us into
						[smaller] groups and each group <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-517" type="subject">wandered</term> in a different direction. The <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-477" type="subject">camp commandant</term> would drive
						around from group to group in a taxi, holding a map in his hand, and wherever the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-477" type="subject">Oberscharführer</term> would order, there they would take us. Usually these were places where the fire of <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1080" type="subject">war</term> was still a little way off. My group numbered 4,000 <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-825" type="subject">women</term>, of which 1,200 survived. Our group
						was mainly Jewish <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-825" type="subject">women</term> from <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/798544/republic-of-poland.html">Poland</placeName> and <placeName
							ref="http://www.geonames.org/8505031/czechoslovakia.html">Czechoslovakia</placeName>. So we <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-517" type="subject">walked on foot</term> for 600 kilometers. We went through all of <placeName
							ref="http://www.geonames.org/2842566/saxony.html">Saxony</placeName>, and together with the <orgName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/authorities/ehri_cb-429">SS men</orgName>
						<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-262" type="subject">hid</term> from the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1078" type="subject">allied armies</term>. When the <orgName
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/authorities/ehri_cb-429">SS men</orgName> no longer had anywhere left to take us, they abandoned us under the open sky and the <term ref="#ehri_et_nationalities_russians">Russians</term>
						<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-573" type="subject">liberated</term> us on <date when="1945-05-07">May 7, 1945</date> (it was a Monday) in <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/2916851/grossdorf.html">Großdorf</placeName> near <placeName
							ref="http://www.geonames.org/2955770/apolda.html">Apolda</placeName> in <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/2842566/saxony.html">Saxony</placeName>.</p>
					<p><persName ref="#ehri_et_amarnikh_rokhl">Rokhel Amarnikh</persName></p>
				</div>
			</div>
